message.body: Crystal, it's Cheryl. ..i tried calling work but I can't talk from the laryngitis. ..I'm really weak ..Up all night with vomiting abs can't keep anything in me. ..can you let George know?
I will. Hope you feel better Cheryl! What a lousy way to start your weekend
Thank you. .i just hope I didn't give it to anyone else
Oh actually, George and Tina aren't in today. Ha!
The deposit bags aren't sealed yet because I had a problem..so the courier won't have to pick anything up. .
No one can get in there unless Patty had a key
I got this. Tina has a key in her office. I'll open up.
Thank you soo much. Call or text me if you need me
Can I deposit the cardiology bags? Did you do anything with them?
Yes.. you can deposit them. .i couldn't get to then yesterday
Okay. I also have a deposit from MRI that's not on the list to accept. I don't know what to do with that
Leave that. .i have to check it
There's money and checks wrapped up in paper.. leave that too
